dct_title_s: Map of the Territory of Minnesota exhibiting the route of the expedition ot the Red River of the north, in the summer of 1849
dct_alternative_sm: Map of the territory of Minnesota exhibiting the route of the expedition to the Red River of the north, in the summer of 1849 / by Capt. John Pope ;drawn by P. S. Morawski.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Shows Minnesota and parts of Wisconsin, Iowa, Nebraska, North Dakota, South Dakota, Manitoba, and Ontario.
Gives both Indian and later place names.
Shows "Proposed line of grants for railroads."
